// Define attributes to apply special behavior
"PAYTABLE ATTRIBUTES" BITFIELD NONE "PAYTABLE ATTRIBUTE LIST" REMOTELY_CONFIGURABLE+OPERATOR_OR_GREATER

// Define maximum total bet for your jurisdiction. This value must come from the MAXIMUM TOTAL BET LIST. It must not exceed 1000.
// The normal value is 20 times the maximum number of lines; in this case, it's 20x30 = 600 which is too low.
// The next number that is below 1000, is 900.
"JURISDICTIONAL MAXIMUM TOTAL BET" NUMERIC 900 UNMODIFIABLE
